WE need to install the following dependcies in our file -

1.Express - main web framework for frontend

2.express-validator - for data validation 

3-bcryptjs- it is used for password encrpytion

4.config- for global variable

5.gravatar- it is used for the profile avatar and use their mail to login and their profile sutomatically get fetech from their mail

6.jsonwebtoken - we need a web token for a validation

7.mongoose- it setup on a database as a layer so we can interact eith the database

8.request - 

there are more dependecy for devloper enviourment 

1. nodemon - it is used to run our server constantly it help to automatically refresh it
 
2. concurrently - it allow us run our server from backend server express and frontend react  